
This django project is created for testing rest api with some customization in imdb api.

app api are with POST method

Search movie by title : localhost:8000/title/
Search movie by id : localhost:8000/id/
Search movie by year : localhost:8000/year/
Search movie by genre : localhost:8000/genre/


to update data ( Genre and Ratings ) give id of the movie Example :

   If you want to update Genre and Ratings of movie who's id is 2.
   use api localhost:8000/update/<id> , where ID is 2. so end input will be localhost:8000/update/2
